<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>모바일 상품권 - GS25</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, target-densitydpi=medium-dpi" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,address=no,email=no" />
	<meta name="description" contents=""/>
	<meta name="keywords" contents=""/>
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.ico">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
	<script src="../../js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="skipMenu"><a href="#container">본문 바로가기</a></div>
	<div class="wrapper">
		<header class="header">
			<h1>모바일 상품권</h1>
			<a href="#" class="btnBack">이전 페이지 이동</a>
			<button type="button" id="qrpop" class="btnQr" title="QR코드 팝업 열기">QR코드</button>
		</header>
		<!-- //header -->
		<section id="container" class="content gs25">
            <!-- 내용 -->
			<div class="stepConArea">
				<!-- step01 -->
				<div class="stepContainer">
					<div class="stepTit">
						<ol>
							<li role="text" aria-current="step">1<span class="hide" role="text">단계</span></li>
							<li role="text">2<span class="hide" role="text">단계</span></li>
						</ol>
						<h2>상품권 등록</h2>
					</div>
					<div class="stepCon">
						<span class="activeInput">
							<label for="barcode">상품권 바코드 숫자입력(12자리)</label>
							<input type="text" id="barcode">
							<button type="button" class="delete">입력 내용 삭제</button>
						</span>
					</div>
					<ul class="notiInfo">
						<li>나만의 냉장고가 아닌곳에서 발급받으신 GS25 상품권 번호를 입력해주세요. 번호는 상품권 바코드 하단에 적힌 12숫자를 입력하시면 됩니다. 일부 외부에서 발급받으신 상품권은 등록이 어려울 수도 있습니다. 자세한 내용은 고객센터를 통해서 안내 받으시기 바랍니다.</li>
						<li>소비자 상담 관련 전화번호 : <a href="tel:1644-5425">1644-5425</a></li>
					</ul>
					<div class="btnFixed">
						<div class="btnPrss">
							<button type="button" class="btnTP active">상품권 조회</button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- //step01 -->
				<!-- step02 -->
				<div class="stepContainer">
					<div class="stepTit">
						<ol>
							<li role="text">1<span class="hide">단계</span></li>
							<li role="text" aria-current="step">2<span class="hide">단계</span></li>
						</ol>
						<h2>보내는 분 정보</h2>
					</div>
					<div class="stepCon">
						<strong class="titDep1">보내는 분</strong>
						<div class="btns">
							<a href="#" role="button" class="btnTS btnS" title="보내는 분 정보 초기화">신규등록</a>
							<a href="#" role="button" class="btnTS btnS">최근주소록</a>
						</div>
						<ul class="formArea">
							<li>
								<span class="activeInput">
									<label for="name02">이름</label>
									<input type="text" id="name02">
									<button type="button" class="delete">입력 내용 삭제</button>
								</span>
							</li>
							<li>
								<div class="inputSel">
									<select title="통신사 선택">
										<option value="">SKT</option>
										<option value="">KT</option>
										<option value="">LGU+</option>
										<option value="">알뜰폰SKT</option>
										<option value="">알뜰폰KT</option>
										<option value="">알뜰폰LGU+</option>
									</select>
									<span class="activeInput">
										<label for="phoneNum02">핸드폰 번호<em>(숫자만 입력)</em></label>
										<input type="number" id="phoneNum02">
										<button type="button" class="delete">입력 내용 삭제</button>
									</span>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="shipSetting">
								<div class="inputSel">
									<input type="text" title="우편번호등록" placeholder="우편번호" disabled>
									<button type="button" class="btnTS btnM active">우편번호 찾기</button>
								</div>
								<input type="text" title="주소등록" placeholder="주소를 입력해주세요." disabled>
								<span class="activeInput">
									<label for="address02">상세주소를 입력해주세요.</label>
									<input type="text" id="address02">
									<button type="button" class="delete">삭제</button>
								</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="btnPrss line">
						<button type="button" class="btnTP">이전</button>
						<button type="button" class="btnTP active">다음</button>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- //step02 -->
			</div>
            <!--//내용 -->
		</section>
		<!-- //container -->
	</div>
	<!-- //wrapper -->
</body>
</html>

